com.samsung.android.sdk.health.content

Interface ShealthAccessControl.AccessRegistrationListener

  • Enclosing class:
    ShealthAccessControl

    public static interface ShealthAccessControl.AccessRegistrationListener
    This listener interface receives the result events for access registration requests. The plug-in application must pass an instance of this interface when calling the registerForPermission() method.
    Author:
    bikashkhetan
